data.text:
NBA news and rumors about Martell Webster

News publishing in english has been temporarely discontinued. You can access here to our news archive. For the latest NBA news, you can visit our NBA news site in spanish.

Injuries

Wizards forward Martell Webster to have season-ending surgery on hip

Wizards forward Martell Webster will undergo surgery Friday in Nashville. He expects to be sidelined four to six months but it could be more.
